show.description: For just one night, the fierce and manipulative Alisha — daughter of a housemaid — forces the innocent Ruhi to pose as her in order to deceive billionaire Aditya. But that night turns into a dangerous illusion — filled with deception, desire, and mistaken identities — because in that world, falling in love... means the end!
